author: Huileng Tan
title: Coronavirus live updates: China reports 63 new cases and 2 deaths, Trump escalates tension with WHO over pandemic
description: China's National Health Commission (NHC) reported 63 new cases and two deaths as of April 8. Of the new cases, the NHC attributed 61 to travelers from overseas.
